Costs are R350 per person for the first abseiling or rock climbing experience, R150 per person for the second and free for the third time. Entrants must remember that there must be four or more people entering. For more information, call or WhatsApp Ryk Diepraam on 083 528 9586, send an email to info@buffalogorge.co.za or get more information on their website at www.buffalogorge.co.za.